==English==
===Etymology===
: [[sneaker]] (to imply being [[carried]]) + [[net]]
===Noun===
'''sneakernet'''
# {{computing}} ''(slang; humerous; archaic)'' A method of transfering [[computer programmes]] from one computer to another that involves a [[person]] carrying one or more items of [[storage media]].  The noun is intended to be a humerous dig at older computers that are not connected to a [[network]].